Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:02.51,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Everything will end, and then it will begin.}šechno skončí a pak začne.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:07.39,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{It's time for us to abandon everything\N and take our first step into a new world.}Je načase, abychom opustili vše a podnikli náš první krok do nového světa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:10.90,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I've been saving Chiyu for this day.}Šetřil jsem Chiyu pro tento den.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:15.90,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Her wisdom will lead us to victory.}Její moudrost nás povede k vítězství.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:18.65,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't accept another failure, Kark.}Nebudu tolerovat další selhání, Karku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:22.66,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Your false understanding will \Nbring about your death.}Vaše falešné pochopení přinese vaši smrt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:26.16,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{I am your comrade, not your subordinate.}Jsem tvůj soudruh, ne podřízený.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:27.37,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{You...}Ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:31.37,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Should we be arguing amongst ourselves?}Měli bychom se hádat mezi sebou?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:36.17,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{You idiots are fighting the wrong enemy.}Vy idioti bojujete se špatným nepřítelem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.34,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Drayle-dono is right.}Drayle má pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:43.43,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{We should be working to defeat Kamina Chihiro.}Měli bychom se zaměřit na odstranění Kamina Chihiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:44.73,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{No!}Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:48.86,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{He killed Aoi Jun and Minakami Haru.}Zabil Aoi Juna a Minakami Harua.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:49.56,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:53.76,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro cut down both of them.}Chihiro je sejmul oba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.64,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You're lying! Chihiro-kun would never—}Lžete! Chihiro by nikdy—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.24,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{They're not the only ones.}Nejsou jediní.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.20,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{He killed thousands of audience members, too.}Taky zabil tisíce členů publika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:07.23,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Ignorance is bliss, but it's terribly sinful.}Nevědomost je blaženost, ale je to hrozně hříšné.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:12.79,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Isn't a father's responsibility\N to explain things to his daughter?}Není otec povinen vysvětlit věci své dceři?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:18.19,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{We were also wrong to use \Nthe concertgoers as a shield.}Také jsme se mýlili, že používáme koncertní diváky jako štít.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:21.76,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{But they knew that and attacked anyway.}Ale oni to věděli a stejně zaútočili.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:25.30,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{It was a display of unbelievable cruelty.}Byl to projev neuvěřitelné krutosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:29.47,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{This is what you call a worst case scenario.}Tomu se říká nejhorší možný scénář.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:34.94,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't know who told them, but they\N must've known this would happen.}Nevím, kdo jim to řekl, ale museli vědět, že k tomu dojde.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:39.87,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Kamina Chihiro has begun to\N awaken as the Lord of Cruelty.}Kamina Chihiro se začala probouzet jako Lord krutosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.36,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Eventually he will destroy everything.}Nakonec vše zničí.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.39,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{No. Chihiro-kun wouldn't hurt anybody...}Ne. Chihiro by nikomu neublížil...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.15,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Drayle took this video.}Drayle získal toto video.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:53.12,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{See for yourself.}Podívej se sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.38,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{The plan was a success.}Plán byl úspěšný.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:03.13,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I destroyed the artificial keystone\N and stopped the Second Great Collapse.}Zničila jsem umělý klíč a zastavila Druhé Velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.72,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You were amazing, Chihiro-san.}Byl jsi úžasný, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:08.76,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You're unstoppable now.}Jsi teď nezastavitelný.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:12.27,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{But a lot of people died.}Ale spousta lidí umřela.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.53,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah, but...}Jo, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:16.73,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{It's the Foundation's fault.}To je chyba Nadace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:20.48,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{If we hadn't stopped them, who knows\N what would've happened to Tokyo.}Pokud bychom je nezastavili, kdo ví co by se stalo s Tokiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.23,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You saved them, Chihiro-san.}Zachránil jsi je, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.08,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kotetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.03,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{It's all thanks to you.}To vše díky tobě.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:31.06,Shinsou main,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{After all, you're the Lord of Vermilion.}Potom všem, jsi Vermilionský lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.17,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{What are you talking about?}O čem to mluvíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:37.49,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{The last surviving vessel\N becomes the Lord of Vermilion.}Poslední přeživší schránka se stane Vermilionským lordem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.66,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Only the last surviving vessel.}Pouze poslední přeživší schránka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:45.33,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{In other words, my meritorious deeds make {\i1{me}{\i0} \N{the best candidate for Lord of Vermilion.}Jinými slovy, mé záslužné skutky {\i1}mě{\i0}  činí nejlepší kandidátkou na Vermilionského lorda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.34,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah, but...}Jo, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:50.16,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihhi's clearly number one.}Chihhi je jednoznačně číslo jedna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:52.19,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Th-That's not...}T-To není...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.43,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Dux-sama!}Paní Dux!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.93,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm glad he's okay.}Jsem ráda, že je v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:09.52,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{It's because Cerdid provided first aid.}To proto, že Cerdid poskytla první pomoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:12.50,Shinsou main,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I was just following Chihiro's orders.}Jen jsem se řídila Chihirovými pokyny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.34,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Thanks, Cerdid.}Děkuju, Cerdid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:22.09,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Shoko's awful, though.}Shoko je strašná.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:26.23,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Didn't she leave the both of them\N to go destroy the artificial keystone?}Neopustila ona snad oba, aby zničila umělý klíč?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:28.59,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Now she's acting like it was her achievement.}Teď se chová jako by to byla její zásluha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.50,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Everyone's different.}Každý je jiný.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:34.31,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's true that she stopped the Great Collapse.}Je pravda, že zastavila Velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.12,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{As long as you're okay with it.}Dokud s tím nemáš problém ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.66,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sure he'll be surprised}Jsem si jistý, že bude překvapenej,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.90,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{to learn he was saved by \N people he was trying to kill.}že byl zachráněn lidmi, které chtěl zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:47.78,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{The smallest thing can \Ndivide enemies and allies.}Nejmenší věc může rozdělit nepřátele a spojence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:52.00,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{There must have been a way\N we could've avoided a fight.}Musí být nějaký způsob, jak bychom se mohli vyhnout boji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:57.26,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Just like he was Akira-san's\N friend, Aoi Jun could've been...}Stejně jako byl přítel Akiry, Aoi Jun by mohl být...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:06.67,sign_8594_73_Kakihara_Isshin_,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Kakihara Isshin    Kurokami Marie    Akaya Inuki    Aoi Jun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.80,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{If only that hadn't happened to Inuki-san...}Kdyby se to tak nestalo Inukimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.49,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm not so sure.}Nejsem si tak jistá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.67,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Jun was one twisted dude.}Jun byl jeden překroucený frajer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:12.07,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{He must feel pretty uncomfortable\N sitting next to Inuki now.}Musí se cítit docela nepříjemně sedět vedle Inukiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.75,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{He wasn't a bad guy.}Nebyl zlý člověk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.57,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{This is my first time here.}Tohle je poprvé co jsem tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:31.91,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Until now, I've allowed you to handle\N everything here without any interference.}Až dosud jsem ti umožnil zvládnout všechno bez jakéhokoli zásahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.04,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{This is...}To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.94,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{This is an impressive recreation.}To je impozantní rekreace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.99,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{The seventh artificial\N keystone was destroyed.}Sedmý umělý klíč byl zničen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.00,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{We can no longer cause a Great Collapse.}Nemůžeme už víc vyvolat Velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:05.08,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{But if we absorb the ley line\N energy at the remaining six}Ale když absorbujeme dráhu energie zbývajících šesti
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:10.32,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{and guide them using this research\N equipment, we can forcibly open gates.}a řídit je pomocí tohoto výzkumného zařízení, můžeme násilně otevřít brány.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:16.01,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{However, forcibly opening\N gates causes a reaction.}Avšak násilně otvírající brány způsobují reakci.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:20.36,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{When Tokyo's energy balance is\N thrown off, it will be destroyed}Pokud bude Tokijská energetická rovnováha rozhozena, bude zničena
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.25,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{and swallowed up by another world.}a pohlcena jiným světem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.46,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you sure?}Jsi si jistá?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.95,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Fantastic.}Fantastické.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:29.39,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I tried so desperately to bring Mitsuki\N back, but it wasn't necessary.}Snažil jsem se tak zoufale přivést Mitsuki zpět, ale to nebylo nutné.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:32.02,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I can simply go meet her myself.}Mohu ji jednoduše potkat osobně.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:35.61,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't care if it means destroying\N Tokyo or the entire world.}Je mi jedno, jestli to znamená zničit Tokio nebo celý svět.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:36.60,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{It's trash.}Je to odpad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.55,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{The Foundation, the Heroic\N Lineage... It's all trash!}Nadace, hrdinská linie... Vše je odpad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.48,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Only you...}Pouze ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:49.49,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Mitsuki, what expression will you make when\N I bring all of Tokyo with me to see you?}Mitsuki, jaký budeš mít výraz když se celé Tokio vrátí se mnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:57.98,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I know. You'll be surprised, then smile.}Vim. Budeš překvapená, potom úsměv.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:08:01.99,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{You'll know it's exactly the kind of\N thing that I—that} {\i1}{we}{\i0} {would do.}Budeš vědět, že to je přesně ta věc, kterou já—to uděláme.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.11,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Begin, Chiyu.}Začni, Chiyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:11.51,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{The fruit of our research is \Nour reunion on the other side.}Ovocem našeho výzkumu je naše shledání na druhé straně.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:18.42,Shinsou main,MACHINE,0000,0000,0000,,{Identity verified.}Identita ověřena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.35,Shinsou main,MACHINE,0000,0000,0000,,{Welcome, Professor Mitsuki.}Vítejte, Profesorko Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:26.37,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Kamina Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.82,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{How dare you embarrass me \Nin front of Dux-sama.}Jak se opovažuješ, abys mě zahanbil před paní Dux.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:35.06,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You stole my praise out from under me.}Ukradl jsi mi moji chválu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:38.90,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Such a coward couldn't possibly\N be the Lord of Vermilion.}Takový zbabělec nemůže být Vermilionským lordem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.08,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't allow it.}Já to nedovolím.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:46.35,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I stopped the Great Collapse.\N I should be the Lord of Vermilion.}Já zastavila Velké zhroucení. Měla bych být Vermilionským lordem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:48.48,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{How dare he?}Jak se opovažuje?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:52.15,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kamina Chihiro is in my way.}Kamina Chihiro mi stojí v cestě.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:54.29,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{If only he'd disappear...}Kdyby zmizel ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:09:00.20,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Only the last surviving vessel can\N become the Lord of Vermilion.}Pouze poslední přeživší schránka se může stát Vermilionským lordem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.40,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Why didn't I notice something so simple sooner?}Proč jsem si něco tak jednoduchého neuvědomila dřív?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:10.32,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll have to kill Kamina Chihiro and the others.}Musím zabít Kamina Chihiru a ostatní.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.18,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's all for Dux-sama.}To vše pro paní Dux.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:18.04,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Then I will be...}Potom budu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.71,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Bloody blessings upon your deeds.}Krvavé požehnání na tvé skutky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.12,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{You're mine!}Jsi můj!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:52.32,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh, man. He killed his own allies.}Člověče. On zabil vlastní spojence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.57,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{He's merciless.}Je nemilosrdnej.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:58.01,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{He kills enemies and \Nallies indiscriminately.}Zabíjí nepřátelé i spojence bez rozdílu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.95,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Perhaps he's been seduced by his own power.}Možná, že byl sveden svou vlastní silou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.34,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't avert your gaze.}Neodkláněj svůj zrak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:07.37,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Isn't Kamina Chihiro important to you?}Není pro tebe Kamina Chihiro důležitý?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.88,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Yahoo!}Juchůů!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.82,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{He knows that thing used to be human.}Ví, že ta věc byla lidská.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:15.16,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You're lying... This is a lie!}Lžeš ... To je lež!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.46,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{It's the undeniable truth.}Je to nepopiratelná pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:19.70,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{No! Chihiro-kun is...}Ne! Chihiro je...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:23.11,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{He's no longer the Kamina Chihiro you know.}Už není ten Kamina Chihiro, kterého znáš.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.67,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I understand how you feel.}Chápu jak se cítíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.98,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{But he's a victim as well.}Ale on je také oběť.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.37,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:37.38,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{The more he uses his power, the more\N the Lord of Vermilion consumes him.}Čím víc používá svou sílu, tím víc ho pohlcuje Vermilionský lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:42.87,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{No one can control the power\N of the Lord of Vermilion.}Nikdo nemůže ovládat sílu Vermilionského lorda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:51.10,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{He continues to climb the stairway to\N destruction without knowing what he's doing.}Stále vylézá po schodišti k ničení, aniž by věděl, co dělá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.84,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Eventually his consciousness\N will be consumed.}Nakonec bude jeho vědomí pohlceno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:57.77,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{He'll simply destroy everything he can.}Jednoduše zničí všechno co může.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.51,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{It's sad.}Je to smutné.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:05.01,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Save him before he destroys the world.}Zachraň ho před zničením světa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.86,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{You're the only one who can do it.}Jsi jediná kdo to dokáže.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.75,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Only me?}Jen já?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:13.80,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop him from becoming the Lord\N of Vermilion and save him.}Zastav ho než se stane Vermilionským lordem a zachraň ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.27,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Only you can do it, Yuri.}Jen ty to dokážeš, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.33,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Save Chihiro-kun?}Zachránit Chihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:20.45,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Save him, Yuri.}Zachraň ho, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:24.03,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Bring back the Kamina Chihiro you know.}Přiveď zpět Kamina Chihira, kterého znáš.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.53,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Save... Chihiro-kun.}Zachránit... Chihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:30.70,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{That's right, Yuri. Save him.}Tak je to správně, Yuri. Zachraň ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.66,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Me...}Já...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.32,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san.}Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:38.46,Shinsou main,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Is this...}Je to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.58,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah. It's definitely her.}Jo. Je to rozhodně její.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.72,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Damn it. Who did this?}Sakra. Kdo to udělal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.21,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Jun and the kid are gone.}Jun a děcko jsou pryč.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:51.01,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{The only ones left at the\N Foundation are Kark and...}Jediný kdo zbyl v Nadaci je Kark a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.49,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{You're all here.}Všichni jste zde.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:01.32,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Since Shoko is gone, I shall tell you.}Protože Shoko je pryč, řeknu ti to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:05.48,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The agents of Chaos have a new plan.}Agenti Chaosu mají nový plán.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:06.53,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Why, you...}Proč, ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:08.53,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.33,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't you feel sad at all?!}Necítíš smutek potom všem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:13.50,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Haven't you been working together?}Nepracovali jste spolu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:20.35,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{They're planning to take all of \NTokyo to another world.}Chtějí vzít celé Tokio do jiného světa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.63,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{What does that mean?}Co to znamená?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.19,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{What's going to happen to Tokyo?}Co bude s Tokiem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:28.59,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sure there will be a price to pay.}Jsem si jistá, že bude zaplacena cena.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:31.00,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{At best, we'll disappear.}Při nejlepším, zmizíme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.36,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{That's not good.}To není dobré.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:34.10,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Why are they doing this?}Proč to dělají?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:35.97,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{That's meaningless.}To je bezvýznamné.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:39.86,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The only question we should be\N asking is if we can stop them.}Jediná otázka, kterou bychom se měli ptát, je, jestli je můžeme zastavit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.57,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Should we be stopping them?}Měli bychom je zastavit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:46.07,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{You're the one who ordered us to destroy Tokyo.}Ty jsi ta, kdo nám přikázal zničit Tokio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:51.96,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Choose your own futures.}Vyberte si svou vlastní budoucnost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:58.23,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{The Lord of Vermilion will erase everything.}Vermilionský lord vymaže vše.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.47,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Even his memories of you.}Dokonce i jeho vzpomínky na tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.38,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Before that happens...}Předtím, než se to stane ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.46,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun...}Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:18.34,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You seem well, Yuri.}Vypadáš dobře, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:20.73,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{So do you.}Ty taky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.11,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I've missed you.}Chyběla jsi mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:27.04,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sorry, but I...}Omlouvám se, ale já...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.48,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's fine.}To je v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:33.77,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Maldeus Church and the AVAL\N Science Foundation can fight,}Maldeuský kostel a Vědecká Nadace AVAL můžou bojovat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.38,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{but that doesn't change our relationship.}ale to nezmění náš vztah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.05,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun...}Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.39,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Want some hot cocoa?}Chtěl bys nějaké horké kakao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:43.44,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{It's pretty close to the flavor\N your mother used to make.}Je to docela blízko k chuti, kterou dělávala tvá matka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.01,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's good.}To je dobrý.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.72,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Really?}Opravdu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.60,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Thanks, Yuri.}Děkuju, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:58.99,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't remember my mom's flavor, but \N drinking your hot chocolate relaxes me.}Nepamatuju si máminu chuť, ale pít horkou čokoládu mě uklidňuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:00.78,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{That's great.}To je skvělé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:04.77,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You haven't changed at all. I'm so glad!}Po tom všem jsi se nezměnil. Jsem tak ráda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:05.51,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.25,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I was really worried.}Mělá jsem vážné obavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:11.21,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I wasn't sure what I'd do if you'd\N become someone else.}Nebyl jsem si jistá co udělám, kdyby ses stal někým jiným.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:12.76,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{But I'm glad.}Ale jsem ráda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:13.49,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:18.45,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I saw a weird vision of you\N becoming the Lord of Vermilion.}Viděla jsem divnou verzi jak jsi se stal Vermilionským lordem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:23.56,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{The concertgoers at the Infinity\N Theater were turned into monsters,}Koncertní diváci v divadle Infinity byly proměněny v monstra,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.28,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{and with incredible power, you...}a s neuvěřitelnou silou jsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:27.51,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I see.}Chápu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.26,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{But I couldn't believe it.}Ale nemohla jsem tomu uvěřit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.51,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I knew it was impossible.}Věděla jsem, že to bylo nemožné.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.27,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I knew it was all a lie.}Věděla jsem, že to jsou všechno lži.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.91,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I was fooled by—}Byla jsem bláhová—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:37.93,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's true.}Je to pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.77,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I killed them. With my hands.}Zabil jsem je. Vlastníma rukama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:43.82,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why?}Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.03,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's Kark's fault.}Je to Karkova chyba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:49.00,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{If he hadn't transformed the concertgoers...}Kdyby nezměnil koncertní diváky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.28,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I had to do it.}Musel jsem to udělat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:54.27,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I had no choice.}Neměl jsem na výběr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:57.45,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You said you wouldn't let anyone else die.}Říkal jsi, že nenecháš nikoho jiného umřít.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.32,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I still feel that way.}Pořád to cítím.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:04.21,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{But to save everyone from the Great\N Collapse, I have to get my hands dirty.}Ale zachránit svět před Velkým zhroucením, musel jsem si ušpinit ruce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:06.17,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{That's what I thought.}To je to, co jsem si myslel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:08.85,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You had to?}Musel jsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.11,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You've changed, Chihiro-kun.}Změnil jsi se, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:12.92,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:17.43,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You're not the Chihiro-kun I know.}Nejsi ten Chihiro, kterého znám.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:22.78,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't, Chihiro-kun.}Přestaň, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.40,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't fight anymore.}Už nebojuj.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.39,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Please!}Prosím!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:28.92,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:35.08,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{If you keep using that power,\N you'll destroy yourself.}Pokud budeš tu sílu používat, zničíš sám sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:37.82,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You'll become someone I don't know.}Staneš se někým koho neznám.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.38,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't stop.}Nemohu přestat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:43.58,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I heard the Foundation is\N putting a new plan into motion.}Slyšel jsem, že nadace učiní nový plán do pohybu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:47.45,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Tokyo itself will be swallowed\N up by another world.}Tokio samotné bude pohlceno jiným světem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.77,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm going to fight.}Chystám se bojovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.92,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I took on the dying wishes of \NInuki-san and Kakihara-san.}Převzal jsem poslední přání Inukiho a pana Kakihary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:56.87,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't run now.}Nemůžu teď utéct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.06,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Who cares about that?}Kdo se o to stará?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.35,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:03.32,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You're the only one I need.}Jsi jediný koho potřebuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:06.03,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll forget about my father.}Zapomenu na svého otce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:08.74,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You should forget about the Lord of Vermilion.}Měl bys zapomenout na Vermilionského lorda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:10.36,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{But Yuri...}Ale Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:14.86,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's abandon everything and go\N someplace no one will find us.}Opusťme všechno a pojďme někam kde nás nikdo nenajde.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:19.22,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Somewhere no one can reach us. Just you and me.}Někam kam se nikdo nedostane. Jen ty a já.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.29,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Okay?}Dobře?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.85,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't do that.}To nemohu udělat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.14,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun...}Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.86,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sorry, Yuri.}Promiň, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:31.91,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{No. Don't do it.}Ne. Nedělej to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:37.55,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I have to save him.}Musím ho zachránit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.80,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I will save Chihiro-kun!}Já Chihira zachráním!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:41.98,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.81,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Only I can stop you!}Jen já tě mohu zastavit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.57,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{So I...}Takže já...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.82,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't hurt Chihiro!}Neubližuj Chihirovi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.10,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't bother.}Je to marné.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.96,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What are you doing?!}Co to děláš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.25,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop, both of you!}Přestaňte, obě!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.26,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.51,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Give up, Yuri.}Vzdej se, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.67,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Stay out of my way.}Jsi mi z cesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:22.52,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{I've been hoping this day would come.}Doufala jsem, že tento den přijde.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.51,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{This is your fault.}Tohle je tvá chyba
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:27.73,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro changed since you came along.}Chihiro se změnil od chvíle, kdy jsi přišla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.98,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Leave me alone.}Nech mě být.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:34.17,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{He began to treat me coldly.}Začal se ke mně chovat chladně.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:38.34,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{He valued his time with you \Nmore than fighting.}Trávil víc času s tebou než bojováním.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:43.12,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro's risking his life!}Chihiro riskuje svůj život!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.91,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{But what if you distract him?}Ale co když ho rozptyluješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.63,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{What if something happens to him?}Co když se mu něco stane?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:51.45,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm a Defender.}Já jsem ochránce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:54.13,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Protecting my master is my duty.}Ochrana mého pána je mou povinností.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:59.05,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Yuri, eventually you'll cause Chihiro's death.}Yuri, nakonec způsobíš Chihirovu smrt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:03.08,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sorry, but I'd give my life to stop you.}Omlouvám se, ale dala bych život abych tě zastavila.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:05.41,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{That's not...}To není...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:08.65,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{You also just want to be\N with Chihiro, don't you?}Taky chceš být s Chihirem, viď?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.31,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{I will kill you.}Zabiju tě.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.81,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't care if Chihiro hates\N me for the rest of his life.}Je mi jedno jestli mě bude Chihiro po zbytek života nenávidět.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:17.65,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't care if he looks at me\N with resentment forever.}Je mi jedno, jestli se na mě dívá s odporem navždy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.66,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You...}Ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:21.42,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't, Cerdid!}Nedělej to, Cerdid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.12,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop! That's an order!}Přestaň! To je rozkaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.75,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sorry, Chihiro!}Omlouvám se, Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.79,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{No...}Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.63,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop!}Přestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:42.58,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.14,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:47.64,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Jak?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.02,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Cerdid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:54.52,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.99,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Cerdid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.41,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No...}Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:07.12,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{N-No. This wasn't...}N-Ne. To nebylo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:10.01,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yuri, why?}Yuri, proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.11,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I didn't do anything.}Nic jsem neudělala.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.38,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun...}Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:18.20,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I wanted to save you.}Chtěla jsem tě zachránit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.09,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:27.10,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why? Why?}Proč? Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:31.60,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't do this anymore.}Už to nemůžu dělat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.73,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's begin.}Začněme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.94,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{All artificial keystones activated.}Všechny umělé klíče aktivovány.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.71,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Ley line energy absorption bulb open.}Baňka na absorbci energetické dráhy otevřena.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.11,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Limiter removed.}Omezovač odstraněn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:44.49,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Contact.}Kontakt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.57,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Dirac value rising.}Dirac hodnota stoupá.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:59.05,Shinsou main,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{Encroaching on dimensional barrier.}Narušení dimenzionální bariéry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:20.19,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{The destruction is finally starting!}Zničení konečně začíná.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.68,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The land I yearn for is on the other side.}Země po které toužím je na druhé straně.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:28.08,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Now is the moment I finally approach}Teď je okamžik, kdy se konečně přiblížím.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.82,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san.}Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:57.58,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Guys...}Lidi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.27,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Where's Cerdid?}Kde je Cerdid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:08.66,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's just us now, but we still have work to do.}Teď je to jen na nás, ale máme stále práci, kterou musíme udělat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.29,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{That's right.}Správně.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:14.80,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The center of the phenomenon\N is the research equipment}Středem tohoto fenoménu jsou výzkumná zařízení
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.46,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{at the AVAL Science Foundation HQ.}ve AVAL Vědecké Nadaci HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:21.20,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The equipment that took your\N mother from you, Kamina Chihiro.}To zařízení ti vzalo tvou matku, Kamina Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:22.92,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Got it.}Chápu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:28.30,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Heaven helps those who help themselves.}Nebe pomáhá těm, kteří si pomáhají.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:31.23,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I hope all's well that ends well.}Doufám, že všechno dobře skončí.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.33,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Right, Chihiro-san?}Správně, Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.08,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's go, everyone.}Pojďme, všichni.
